  <thing id="pPTMighSum" name="Path Ability: Mighty Summons" description="Any creatures you summon using {i}summon monster{/i} or {i}summon nature&apos;s ally {/i}spells receive 2 bonus hit points per Hit Die and DR 5/magic. Whenever you use one of these spells to summon more than one creature, you receive one additional creature of the same type. When casting such a spell to summon just one creature, you can expend one use of mythic power to give it the agile or savage mythic simple template (see pages 47-48)." compset="InPlay">
